    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a vehicle in peerless condition. This unit has been meticulously preserved to a standard that mirrors its original showroom debut, offering a level of refinement and mechanical integrity that is increasingly rare on the market. From the pristine exterior finish to the flawless, smoke-free interior, every detail reflects a history of uncompromising care. For the discerning driver seeking showroom-quality excellence and long-term value, this represents the definitive choice in its class.",
