    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m finally letting go of my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been garage-kept and pampered since day one\u2014honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! The paint has that deep, mirror-like shine, the interior is absolutely pristine, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve been meticulous with the maintenance because I truly love this car, and it shows. It\u2019s rare to find one kept in this kind of condition, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by for a coffee and a look\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love with it just like I did!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
